---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Stay for Health Journeys — Preserve Yourself While You Can">
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-24">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-narrow text-center">
        <p class="text-ember text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4">For Those Facing Uncertainty</p>
        <h1 class="heading-lg mb-6">
          For when time<br/>
          <span class="text-ember">becomes precious.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="body-lg text-parchment-muted max-w-xl mx-auto">
          For parents with young children. For those facing diagnoses. For anyone who understands that tomorrow isn't promised. Your voice can be a gift that lasts forever.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sensitive Intro -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-void-50">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <div class="bg-void p-8 border border-ember/30 text-center">
          <p class="body-lg italic font-serif text-parchment mb-4">
            "My daughter is only three. If something happens to me, I want her to know who I was. To hear my voice telling her I love her. To have advice from me for moments I might not be there for."
          </p>
          <p class="text-parchment-muted">This is why Stey exists.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Use Cases -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <h2 class="heading-md text-center mb-12">For life's most important moments</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">New Parents</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted">
              Record messages for future birthdays, graduations, weddings. Create a voice your children can grow up with, even in the worst-case scenarios no parent wants to imagine.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Facing a Diagnosis</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted">
              When facing serious illness, capture yourself while you can. Your voice, your laugh, your stories — preserved for those who will need to remember you.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Early Memory Concerns</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted">
              For those in early stages of cognitive decline, capture memories, relationships, and life stories while they're still clear. Create a record that preserves your essence.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">High-Risk Occupations</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted">
              Military, first responders, dangerous professions — those who face risk daily and want their families to have their voice, just in case.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What to Record -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-void-50">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <h2 class="heading-md text-center mb-8">Messages that matter</h2>
        <p class="body-lg text-center text-parchment-muted mb-12">
          What would you want your children to hear from you, even if you're not there?
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-void p-6 border border-void-200">
            <p class="font-serif text-lg text-ember">"Here's what I want you to know about who I am and what I believe..."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-void p-6 border border-void-200">
            <p class="font-serif text-lg text-ember">"When you're struggling, remember this..."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-void p-6 border border-void-200">
            <p class="font-serif text-lg text-ember">"Here's the story of how I met your mom/dad..."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-void p-6 border border-void-200">
            <p class="font-serif text-lg text-ember">"On your wedding day, I want you to hear this..."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-void p-6 border border-void-200">
            <p class="font-serif text-lg text-ember">"The proudest moment of my life was..."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-void p-6 border border-void-200">
            <p class="font-serif text-lg text-ember">"Here's how much I love you, in my own voice..."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Privacy Note -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mb-3">Your most personal thoughts, completely private</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted">
              These recordings contain your most intimate thoughts and feelings. Stey processes everything on your device — no cloud, no servers, no one listening. Your legacy belongs to you and whoever you choose to share it with.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-void-50">
      <div class="container-narrow text-center">
        <h2 class="heading-md mb-6">
          Don't wait for "someday."<br/>
          <span class="text-ember">Someday is today.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="body-lg text-parchment-muted mb-8">
          The best time to start recording was yesterday. The second best time is now.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-parchment text-void px-8 py-4 font-medium hover:bg-ember transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.81-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/>
          </svg>
          Download for iOS — Free
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
